By your unverified statistics there is 1 death per 9333   guns  . FARS (  http://www-fars.nhtsa.dot.gov/Main/index.aspx  ) reported that in 2007 there was 1 death per 5523 cars. A car is 59% more likely to kill then a gun.Ban cars instead.